						               													<description>The first of its kind - a squishy dice throwing and rolling strategy party game!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Asteroid Dice came about from a love of dice and dodgeball! A dicey combination? We don&amp;rsquo;t think so. Simply throw and collide your squishy foam dice to roll the highest score each round and win all the cards in the asteroid field. You must choose a dice from the middle of the table, but if you pick the same as someone else, then battle it out to see who gets that dice and who loses their card!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;How to play: Place all the giant squishy dice in the center of the table and take your deck of cards. Secretly choose which dice card you want to play, and on the count of 3 reveal it to the other players. Grab the dice you chose and prepare to roll them! If anyone matches their cards, you brawl with the chosen dice.The last player hit will gain their opponent&amp;rsquo;s cards and the losers have to choose from the leftover dice. Now everyone rolls their dice in turn - starting with the D20 and down to the D6 with the highest number winning. But watch out for the special cards! Losteroid cards are blackholes that will suck all the cards away in the round and reduce your score if you end up with one in your score pile. Play your &amp;quot;I Can&amp;rsquo;t Diecide&amp;quot; card if you&amp;rsquo;re not sure which dice to choose or as part of your dice game strategy.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
